{"tid":1025713,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"樓市剛性需求即係投資需求","createTime":"2019-02-17T14:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T01:58:20.000Z","uid":80972,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"047c74c67413a0860f77c966115ae9eb3fee5707","tid":1025713,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:03:05.000Z","msg":"成日講嘅剛性需求6成都係非自住<br />\n個數字仲要係2016年，2019年分分鐘可能到7成以上<br />\n投資需求就係，買就一齊高追，放就一齊踩多2腳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3CqjFHf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3CqjFHf.jpg&h=6fb05431&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過完年後，中國經濟壞消息慢慢出黎<br />\n到時又係另一個跌浪"},{"pid":"31e697006289053e024311180a0419cee41a76f6","tid":1025713,"uid":35941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:08:52.000Z","msg":"即6成人係租租囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60951daaeb30684b0cd0daafc3e29808bc4b275c","tid":1025713,"uid":6624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:09:04.000Z","msg":"講緊一手細單位 你完全唔提"},{"pid":"aa777b4cbc9f21d7c33fbbb7aeb98274afba3c47","tid":1025713,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:52:02.000Z","msg":"環海．東岸 好多成交<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7c593b9008a44e332e62b8b892870e4355d411","tid":1025713,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:52:52.000Z","msg":"紅磡環海．東岸進入收樓高峰期，二手轉讓個案急增，市場首錄樓花摸貨轉讓個案。1A座中層A室，實用面積296平方呎，屬於1房間隔，原業主2015年10月以513萬元購入，尚未與發展商完成交易，便以確認人身份把單位以530萬轉售，成為罕有樓花摸貨個案。<br />\n據了解，環海．東岸屬於舊契項目，不受禁止樓花摸貨限制，而原業主持貨3年餘，帳面獲利約17萬元，期內升值約3.3%；若扣除厘印費（15.4萬）及代理佣金等雜項支出，估計實質損失約4萬元離場。"},{"pid":"1e6dbd5a57b7abb62cae5b81e72a3e3b0f7daead","tid":1025713,"uid":80972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"60951daaeb30684b0cd0daafc3e29808bc4b275c","tid":1025713,"uid":6624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:09:04.000Z","msg":"講緊一手細單位 你完全唔提"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T17:15:10.000Z","msg":"430都有2房啦<br />\n香港3,4人家庭都夠住<br />\n最有代表性啦<br />\n<br />\n如果你有數據，你咪講埋大單位囉"},{"pid":"a3c338f25e4e0390d568eb2a2a96c6070c640c8d","tid":1025713,"uid":170079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T17:31:40.000Z","msg":"剛需就從來都係得啖笑架喇<br />\n你試下依家學大陸咁玩限賣限價<br />\n你睇仲有無人買樓?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64a328fbd3b8e7031f3ca8d12d52bdad08ce47f","tid":1025713,"uid":182330,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T17:32:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"753ea82788d0aec5be4c55af24ec585ed30ea469","tid":1025713,"uid":51294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d64a328fbd3b8e7031f3ca8d12d52bdad08ce47f","tid":1025713,"uid":182330,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T17:32:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T17:36:51.000Z","msg":"冇錯，聽日港府就公布大灣區，國家同香港發展只會越嚟越好，樓價大漲小回，遲D升到連大陸樓都買唔起就唔好冤自己點解租一世樓喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a2bc76fda846e5b81b99ad8666c15b2d84e780","tid":1025713,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"753ea82788d0aec5be4c55af24ec585ed30ea469","tid":1025713,"uid":51294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d64a328fbd3b8e7031f3ca8d12d52bdad08ce47f","tid":1025713,"uid":182330,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T17:32:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T17:36:51.000Z","msg":"冇錯，聽日港府就公布大灣區，國家同香港發展只會越嚟越好，樓價大漲小回，遲D升到連大陸樓都買唔起就唔好冤自己點解租一世樓喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:08:21.000Z","msg":"我驚你開口中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08638121a823d5bbdf9674f52607dc8c29ed9a11","tid":1025713,"uid":51294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59a2bc76fda846e5b81b99ad8666c15b2d84e780","tid":1025713,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s